H0.text: Which country is bordered by Latvia to the north, Ukraine to the south, and Poland to the west. Lithuania

H1.text: Which country is bordered by Latvia to the north, Ukraine to the south, and Poland to the west. Russia

H3.text: Which country is bordered by Latvia to the north, Ukraine to the south, and Poland to the west. Belarus

A4.text: Belarus borders five countries: Latvia to the north, Lithuania to the northwest, Poland to the west, Russia to the north and the east, and Ukraine to the south.
